{"id": 59693, "date": "2025-09-20T04:00:19", "date_gmt": "2025-09-20T11:00:19", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59693"}, "modified": "2026-05-24T21:54:38", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-25T04:54:38", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-september-20-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/09/20/kingdom-of-days-september-20-2/", "title": {"rendered": "September 20"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1968:\u00a0</strong>Earth plays a gig at Le Teendezvous in New Shrewsbury, New Jersey. (Note: Brucebase places this show on this date, but local press advertisements suggest it did not take place, at least not tonight. Consider this one suspect.)</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4379\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1968-0920/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1968-0920.jpg?fit=524%2C782&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"524,782\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1968-0920\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1968-0920.jpg?fit=524%2C782&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4379 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1968-0920.jpg?resize=524%2C782&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"524\" height=\"782\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1968-0920.jpg?w=524&amp;ssl=1 524w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1968-0920.jpg?resize=201%2C300&amp;ssl=1 201w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 524px) 100vw, 524px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1969:\u00a0</strong>Child plays their second of two nights at the Free University in Richmond. Listen to this show&#8211;the earliest known Child recording&#8211;below.</p>\n<div id=\"v-oMbk0dT7-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/oMbk0dT7?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1974:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the new E Street Band play a sold-out show at Philadelphia&#8217;s Tower Theater.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4387\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1974-0920/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1974-0920.jpg?fit=800%2C522&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"800,522\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1974-0920\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1974-0920.jpg?fit=758%2C495&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4387 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1974-0920.jpg?resize=758%2C495&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"495\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1974-0920.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1974-0920.jpg?resize=300%2C196&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1974-0920.jpg?resize=768%2C501&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1975:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play\u00a0 at Grinnell College in Iowa, their first-ever show in that state.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29476\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-0920-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1975-0920.jpg?fit=811%2C1200&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"811,1200\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-0920\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1975-0920.jpg?fit=692%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-29476 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1975-0920.jpg?resize=758%2C1122&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1122\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1975-0920.jpg?w=811&amp;ssl=1 811w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1975-0920.jpg?resize=203%2C300&amp;ssl=1 203w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1975-0920.jpg?resize=692%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 692w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1975-0920.jpg?resize=768%2C1136&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21262\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1975-09-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-20.jpg?fit=2429%2C1628&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2429,1628\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599833520&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1975-09-20\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-20.jpg?fit=758%2C508&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21262 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-20.jpg?resize=758%2C508&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"508\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-20.jpg?w=2429&amp;ssl=1 2429w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-20.jpg?resize=300%2C201&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-20.jpg?resize=1024%2C686&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-20.jpg?resize=768%2C515&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-20.jpg?resize=1536%2C1029&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-20.jpg?resize=2048%2C1373&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1975-09-20.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Another stellar show from the Darkness Tour&#8217;s homecoming stand at the Capitol Theater in Passaic, available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series. Not only do we have yet another fully pro-shot video of this show, we also have a recording of the soundcheck, which has some fascinating covers and the earliest known version of a prototypical &#8220;The Ties That Bind.&#8221; The show itself features the tour premiere of &#8220;Santa Claus is Comin&#8217; to Town&#8221; and a continually evolving &#8220;Point Blank,&#8221; played here with its instrumental introduction for the first time.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Sj6CyZFOwkw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDSj6CyZFOwkw\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-PTgkEwYj-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/PTgkEwYj?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/l7EAGg8zdrE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uzgpF_ANDSU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1982:</strong> Bruce releases his sixth studio album,\u00a0<em>Nebraska.</em></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=OLAK5uy_mP8T22kYL-tavvs0Mrd9UeFWZK2kUH1_Y\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21308\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1982-09-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1982-09-20.jpg?fit=2424%2C1598&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2424,1598\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600089580&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1982-09-20\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1982-09-20.jpg?fit=758%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21308 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1982-09-20.jpg?resize=758%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1982-09-20.jpg?w=2424&amp;ssl=1 2424w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1982-09-20.jpg?resize=300%2C198&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1982-09-20.jpg?resize=1024%2C675&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1982-09-20.jpg?resize=768%2C506&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1982-09-20.jpg?resize=1536%2C1013&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1982-09-20.jpg?resize=2048%2C1350&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1982-09-20.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"54487\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/lexington_herald_leader_1982_09_26_45/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lexington_Herald_Leader_1982_09_26_45-scaled.jpg?fit=2261%2C2560&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2261,2560\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Lexington_Herald_Leader_1982_09_26_45\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lexington_Herald_Leader_1982_09_26_45-scaled.jpg?fit=758%2C859&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-54487 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lexington_Herald_Leader_1982_09_26_45-scaled.jpg?resize=758%2C858&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"858\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lexington_Herald_Leader_1982_09_26_45-scaled.jpg?w=2261&amp;ssl=1 2261w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lexington_Herald_Leader_1982_09_26_45-scaled.jpg?resize=265%2C300&amp;ssl=1 265w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lexington_Herald_Leader_1982_09_26_45-scaled.jpg?resize=904%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 904w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lexington_Herald_Leader_1982_09_26_45-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C870&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lexington_Herald_Leader_1982_09_26_45-scaled.jpg?w=1516&amp;ssl=1 1516w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984: </strong>In town a day early for his Born in the U.S.A. Tour stop, Bruce makes his second guest appearance with the Iron City Houserockers (fronted by Joe Grushecky in one of the band&#8217;s final performances) at the Pennsylvania Decade in Pittsburgh.</p>\n<p><strong>1993:\u00a0</strong>Patti Scialfa appears on\u00a0<em>The Late Show with David Letterman,\u00a0</em>promoting her recent\u00a0<em>Rumble Doll</em> album and performing &#8220;Lucky Girl.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-3ZCFGfGj-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/3ZCFGfGj?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1994:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and Paul Rodgers join John Fogerty on stage at the House of Blues in West Hollywood for &#8220;In the Midnight Hour.&#8221;</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21263\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1994-09-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1994-09-20.jpg?fit=2426%2C1532&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2426,1532\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599834021&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1994-09-20\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1994-09-20.jpg?fit=758%2C479&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21263 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1994-09-20.jpg?resize=758%2C479&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"479\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1994-09-20.jpg?w=2426&amp;ssl=1 2426w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1994-09-20.jpg?resize=300%2C189&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1994-09-20.jpg?resize=1024%2C647&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1994-09-20.jpg?resize=768%2C485&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1994-09-20.jpg?resize=1536%2C970&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1994-09-20.jpg?resize=2048%2C1293&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1994-09-20.jpg?w=2274&amp;ssl=1 2274w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1999: </strong>Bruce and the reunited E Street Band play their third of six nights in Philadelphia on the Reunion Tour, where Bruce improvises a new verse for &#8220;Working on the Highway.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-cbcMa6fr-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/cbcMa6fr?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/qZAGW7nUGXM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"v-CBhRcW0u-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/CBhRcW0u?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>Bruce films the official video for &#8220;Lonesome Day&#8221; in Asbury Park with director Mark Pellington, performing the lead vocals live on every take&#8211;<em>for sixteen hours</em>.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SAMkFVJ-ews?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2003: </strong>Buffalo gets one of the best and certainly the most surprising shows from the Rising Tour stadium leg at the Darien Lake Performing Arts Center. Bruce opens with the tour premiere of &#8220;Tunnel of Love&#8221; and debuts the as-yet-unreleased outtake, &#8220;County Fair.&#8221; &#8220;Mansion on the Hill&#8221; is also tour premiered, and &#8220;Leap of Faith&#8221; makes a return appearance. By now, it&#8217;s apparent to all that Bruce is deliberately unearthing material he hasn&#8217;t touched in years (if at all), and when his upcoming compilation album, <em>The Essential Bruce Springsteen</em> track list is announced, it becomes clear why.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/I21wWMXEvjw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2006:\u00a0</strong>Bruce rehearses with the Sessions Band for their upcoming European tour.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21264\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2006-09-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2006-09-20.jpg?fit=1651%2C1644&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1651,1644\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1599834472&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2006-09-20\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2006-09-20.jpg?fit=758%2C755&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21264 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2006-09-20.jpg?resize=758%2C755&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"755\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2006-09-20.jpg?w=1651&amp;ssl=1 1651w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2006-09-20.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2006-09-20.jpg?resize=1024%2C1020&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2006-09-20.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2006-09-20.jpg?resize=768%2C765&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2006-09-20.jpg?resize=1536%2C1529&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/2006-09-20.jpg?resize=50%2C50&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>Bruce premieres a new concept, playing a full album start-to-finish in select shows. Kicking off at the United Center in Chicago, Bruce and the band play\u00a0<em>Born to Run</em> in full, with Richard Davis and Curt Ramm as guest musicians. The encores are pretty great too, featuring tour premieres of &#8220;Da Doo Ron Ron&#8221; and &#8220;Rockin&#8217; Robin,&#8221; and a rare &#8220;I&#8217;m Goin&#8217; Down.&#8221; In the soundcheck, Bruce works on a new song to be debuted later in the month at Giants Stadium.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0Vk6rblSo_4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/qlIbQ_X-MK8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YkFBFFEUPQo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29479\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2009-09-20a-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2009-09-20a.jpg?fit=651%2C1890&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"651,1890\" data-comments-ope